        "committer": {
          "name": "Li Wei",
          "email": "wei.g.li@intel.com",
          "date": "2013-03-26 02:33:44.000000000",
          "tz": 480
        },
        "subject": "LU-2783 ofd: Implement OBD_IOC_GET_OBJ_VERSION",
        "message": "LU-2783 ofd: Implement OBD_IOC_GET_OBJ_VERSION\n\nThis patch implements OBD_IOC_GET_OBJ_VERSION for ofd, so that tests\ncan use \"lctl getobjversion\" on OST objects.  jt_get_obj_version() now\ntakes ID and group pairs, as well as FIDs, for OST objects.  Although\nthe code are for testing purposes only, dereferencing an ioc_inlbuf\nwithout checking its size is still unacceptable.  Hence,\nmdt_ioc_version_get() is changed to check sizes first.\n\nSigned-off-by: Li Wei <wei.g.li@intel.com>\nChange-Id: If259aeca281dcb3f4ee4dc719719f722cf72cad4\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
